<div class="_pmvv-vidbox-desc">
<h1 id="overlay-title">GHOSTS!</h1>
<p id="overlay-descrip" class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
The invisible SpongeBob and Patrick trick Bikini Bottom into thinking they're haunted by ghosts.	</p>
<div class="rating-row" data-video-id="9sydh5">
<input type="hidden" name="is_logged_in" value="0">
